casebody.data:
Niels CHRISTENSEN, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. BRAGG-KLIESRATH CORPORATION, Defendant-Appellee. No. 6595. Circuit Court of Appeals, Seventh Circuit. June 8, 1938.

Before SPARKS and TREANOR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

On motion of counsel for appellee, it is ordered by this Court that this appeal be, and the same is hereby, dismissed, with costs.
